Basic Commands:
-shut down: sudo shutdown -h now
-reboot: sudo reboot -h now
-settings: sudo raspi-config
-update: sudo apt-get update
-upgrade: sudo apt-get upgrade
-create a folder/directory: mkdir [name]
-check OS: cat /etc/os-release

Coding:
-accessing folder: cd /home/pi/Documents
-create source file: sudo nano [filename].c
-view source file: cat [filename].c
-compiling a program: gcc -o [filename] [filename].c
-running a program: sudo ./[filename]

Camera Setup:
-install packages: sudo apt-get python3-picamera
-camera connection: vcgencmd get_camera
-take picture: raspistill -o cam.jpg